gameoflife.py --help

Usage: gameoflife.py [options]

Conway's Game of life

Options:
  --version        show program's version number and exit
  -h, --help       show this help message and exit
  --width=WIDTH    Field width
  --height=HEIGHT  Field height
  --size=SIZE      Cell size
  --delay=DELAY    Update delay
  --debug          Debug flag


Set cell with mouse and press *Enter* to start a game. You can set random glyders with *r* key. *Esc* for exit.